-- Australia, China Plan Feasibility Study for Carbon Capture-Storage Project
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 2010-12-17T00:21:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-17/australia-china-plan-feasibility-study-for-carbon-capture-storage-project.html
Australia and China have agreed to
cooperate on a feasibility study towards a commercial-scale
carbon capture and storage project in China, Energy Minister
Martin Ferguson said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  